{
  "texts": [
    "We added the industry-specific time trends to the benchmark regression model to avoid results bias caused by this situation.",
    "Construction variable Ln i ×t.",
    "Here, Ln i is the industry classification dummy variable divided by the Ministry of Environmen- tal Protection of China to disclose environmental protection information in 2010.",
    "If the sample industry belongs to i, the value is 1; otherwise, it is 0.",
    "Furthermore, t represents the year variable."
  ]
}